course.content:
```java
static int somme(int a, int b) {
    return a + b;
}
```

Une méthode `static` est appelable directement depuis `main`.

exercises.correction:
public class Main {
    static int somme(int a, int b) { return a + b; }
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println(somme(3, 4));
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] t = {5, 10, 15};
        for (int x : t) System.out.println(x);
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] t = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
        int total = 0;
        for (int x : t) total += x;
        System.out.println(total);
    }
}
